{
  "stem": "24195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But people did know about the concentration camp, had heard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somebody knew somebody who had-- maybe even a guard there or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People had-- knew about this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all we knew is that those camps were, you know-- pretty-- pretty sinister.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were pretty-- you know, where people would probably be tortured and killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did not really know about the mass-- I mean, nobody really realized at the time, in '43 and '44, at the mass exterminations of Jewish people-- of the burning and the gassing them, and then burning the ashes in those big ovens.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they did-- no, that was not really-- but they knew the terrible-- people had some [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] idea that there were terrible things going on.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They just didn't know all the details.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You knew they didn't come back?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you know they wouldn't come back?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because nobody expected them back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were incarcerated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As long as the Nazi Germany is in charge of-- you know, as long as they're in power, they wouldn't be coming back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, you know, nobody was questioning why-- if they-- why they haven't come back yet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they knew as long as this state, this regime is in power, there will nothing change.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was an-- hanging over our heads, this threat that, if you don't do the work, you know-- but it was-- If you don't do the work, then what?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you don't do the work, you may be-- you may be sent to a place worse than this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this camp wasn't that worse-- wasn't that bad, I mean.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't-- there weren't that many-- you know-- we were-- we were guarded, but there was-- there was no wall or barbed wire around our compound.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
